name: NonVisiblePunks
description:
Inspired by CryptoPunks, the Non-Visible Punks are an un-official collection of 7,777 pixelated PNGs at 2048x2048 px resolutions randomly generated and minted through ERC-721 standard on Polygon network. 
Hidden in the blockchain, Non-Visible Punks can barely be seen, but can be collected, mint yourself from www.nonvisiblepunks.com or trade on OpenSea.
